frames.caption: A lone figure walks down a rain-soaked city street illuminated by vibrant neon lights. The scene is set in a futuristic urban environment with towering skyscrapers and digital billboards. The atmosphere is moody and cinematic, enhanced by the reflections on the wet pavement.
frames.description: The image depicts a cyberpunk-style cityscape at night, characterized by heavy rain and bright neon signage. The setting suggests a futuristic metropolis with a blend of modern and dystopian elements.
